ygData.msgSnippet: You shouldn t have any problem there although you you ll want to head over to SK during the day to kill some birdies since the daylight spawns gnolls that
ygData.messageBody:
You shouldn't have any problem there although you you'll want to head over
to SK during the day to kill some birdies since the daylight spawns gnolls
that probably won't give you much exp if any at all.

At your level, I spent a ton of time in Rathe Mountains killing tibrinn
ember (although he is too buffed now for anyone below 40 from what I hear),
unkempt preservers, giant skels, and ebon drakes
